2026-05-10T22:32:30.5431007Z 12    <!--
2026-05-10T22:32:30.5431352Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T22:32:30.5431676Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-10T22:32:30.5432390Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-10T22:32:30.5432732Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-10T22:32:30.5433134Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
